save you from the ensnaring trap!

778
01:18:24,780 --> 01:18:29,408
He will instruct His angels in your
behalf to guard you in all your ways.

779
01:18:33,250 --> 01:18:38,267
I say to you in the name of God,
leave this flesh!

780
01:18:38,268 --> 01:18:41,701
Abyzou!

781
01:18:48,022 --> 01:18:51,309
He will save you from
the destruction and pestilence.

782
01:18:59,005 --> 01:19:06,543
Abyzou!

783
01:19:10,406 --> 01:19:13,963
You are cast away
from the eyes of God!

784
01:19:13,963 --> 01:19:15,326
Daddy!

785
01:19:15,327 --> 01:19:18,562
Abyzou!

786
01:20:06,989 --> 01:20:08,296
Hannah?

787
01:20:11,104 --> 01:20:12,847
Daddy...

788
01:20:16,664 --> 01:20:18,142
It's okay.

789
01:20:58,890 --> 01:20:59,814
Hi.

790
01:21:42,919 --> 01:21:47,465
Oh, it's just a cough.

791
01:21:57,760 --> 01:22:01,069
Tzadok, hey!
I'm calling to say thank you.

792
01:22:01,070 --> 01:22:05,497
Clyde! I was going to call.
I need to get your car back to you.

793
01:22:05,498 --> 01:22:08,529
You keep it.
I am not gonna be going anywhere.

794
01:22:09,479 --> 01:22:10,516
How's the family?

795
01:22:10,517 --> 01:22:13,339
Perfect. More than perfect.

796
01:22:14,011 --> 01:22:16,673
-So what are you gonna do with it?
-I'm not sure.

797
01:22:16,674 --> 01:22:19,907
I'm gonna speak with my father.
We'll find a safe place for it.

798
01:22:19,908 --> 01:22:22,925
Okay. Goodbye, Tzadok.

799
01:22:22,926 --> 01:22:24,506
Goodbye, Clyde.

